Add git-pull-request-message: Generate PR descriptions from commits.

Generates Azure DevOps pull request messages by parsing git log.

Usage: git pull-request-message [target-ref]
- Defaults to HEAD if no target specified
- Generates formatted list from main..target-ref (or main..HEAD)
- Format: '- ##<subject>' with body text on following lines

Output can be directly copied into Azure DevOps PR description, providing
a structured summary of all commits in the PR at a glance.

/Claude-haiku@4.5

Note that none of this is particularly ADO exclusive
